metadata.name: Zodiac Beauty - Unrevealed
metadata.description: Zodiac Beauties are a collection created to celebrate beautifully unique, diverse, astrologically aligned women of the universe. Our collection of 4,444 aims to celebrateall women especially our astrologists, oracles, and all those with their chakras aligned. All of our traits are hand drawn first to capture an advanced level of precision, but at the same time creating a perfectly imperfect collection.
